  "body": "This PR is for review visibility only. It shows the changes made since the baseline commit (234aac5) for the M0–M2 PoC:\n\n- Scaffolded extension + vanilla webview\n- Implemented Extension Host ConnectionManager (HTTP + WS)\n- Chat UI with Send/Stop; status indicator\n- Persist conversationId in workspaceState\n- Exponential backoff reconnect and auto-retry; Stop -> pause\n\nBase branch is a frozen baseline created at 234aac5. Target branch is develop (current working branch).\n\nCo-authored-by: openhands <openhands@all-hands.dev>",
